        // [GIVEN] Invoices "X", "Y" and "Z" for Customer "C" with Amount = 100 each
        // [GIVEN] Cassie selects invoice "X" and "Y" invoices to post
        // [WHEN] Cassie confirms she wants to post 2 out 3 invoices
